    schema1:description "Rachel Hanger is a Partner and UK Head of Investment Management & Funds Tax at KPMG London. Rachel advises traditional, hedge fund managers and pension funds on corporate/partnership, product and operational tax issues. Prior to joining KPMG Rachel was Head of Tax at M&G for over 10 years. She was responsible for providing pro-active tax advice to all parts of M&G’s business particularly focusing on product development, risk and operational tax matters."@en ;
